#--[ TEA Program Signature Analyzer v1 ]---#
# Will analyze any given/input (a TEA program),
# and return its corresponding
# Command+Qualifier Modal Sequence Statistic
# which tells us which TEA command & qualifiers
# are most used in that given program.
# This is basic TEA code static analysis.
############################################
h!:{\|}|d:{\|}|k:{:}|d.::.* | u!:

# for example, will return the following signature
# for this very TEA program:
# !dhk. u
